  <div class="col-md-10">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div class="panel panel-primary mt5 ml5">
              <div class="panel-heading" style="padding: 10px">Passenger Lists</div>
              <!--<div class="panel-body"><b>Passenger Travel Lists</b></div>--> 
            </div>
            <div class="row col-md-12"> You can create a master list of all passengers who are likely to travel on the tickets booked by you, so that while booking tickets you can easily input data from this list.
              Please click on "Add Names" and enter the details of possible passengers in the format given.
              You can add any number of passengers in this master list; however, as per Railway rules, a maximum of only 6 names can be included in any one Passenger Travel List for a specific journey.</div>
         
